Clock Widget - the app with the most detailed and stylish clocks for your home screen! Choose the desired widget style from our catalog. 

The clocks looks like a real one!

Big choice:
- Flip clocks;
- Digital clocks;
- Old School clocks;
- clocks with calendar;
and the most trending widgets!

Widget Clocks are available in 3 sizes and on iOS 14+.
Installation is very easy! Activate the clock in the app and add a widget to your home screen wherever you want!

App is completely free with transparent demo badge on active widget. You can unlock premium remove this badge.

